Package controller

Class UserAlbumsController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.UserAlbumsController
  • public class UserAlbumsController
extends java.lang.Object
    The UserAlbumsController class is responsible for handling user interactions for the scene UserAlbums (UserAlbums.fxml). This scene occurs when the user logs in and is not an Admin.
    Author:
    Vincent Phung, William McFarland
